name: Level Six Storm 1.2mm Leggings - Women's
description: First one in, and the last one out. These neoprene leggings are stretchy and comfortable to move in. They add just enough insulation to turn quick dips into longer paddles or tours. A high waist and raw-cut ankles keep them in place without chafing.1.2mm neoprene is supple and stretchy while adding light insulation in the water.Gusseted crotch improves mobility.Raw-cut ankles fit smoothly.High elastic waist.
